<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">If you worked at Pfizer Inc. in 2021, and you =
got early notice of Pfizer=E2=80=99s successful clinical trial of Paxlovid,=
 its Covid-19 treatment, you could have bought call options on Pfizer=E2=80=
=99s stock and made a lot of money when the results were announced and the =
stock went up. And then you would have gotten very arrested, because that=
=E2=80=99s illegal insider trading. And in fact a Pfizer employee allegedly=
 did do=C2=A0that, and <a href=3D"https://link.mail.bloombergbusiness.com/c=
lick/34412285.257387/aHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuYmxvb21iZXJnLmNvbS9vcGluaW9uL2FydGljbG=
VzLzIwMjMtMDctMDMvaW5zaWRlci10cmFkaW5nLWlzLWJldHRlci1mcm9tLWhvbWU_Y21waWQ9Q=
kJEMDIyMDI0X01PTkVZU1RVRkYmdXRtX21lZGl1bT1lbWFpbCZ1dG1fc291cmNlPW5ld3NsZXR0=
ZXImdXRtX3Rlcm09MjQwMjIwJnV0bV9jYW1wYWlnbj1tb25leXN0dWZm/607f07ceef4b8524a3=
19a23cBc160c86d" itemprop=3D"StoryLink" itemscope=3D"itemscope" target=3D"_=
blank" style=3D"color: #000000; text-decoration: none !important; border-bo=
ttom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: #000000; border-bottom-style: solid; =
background-color: #ccc;">  got arrested</a>.</p>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;"><em>Or</em>=C2=A0you could have bought call op=
tions on Royal Caribbean Cruise Ltd.=E2=80=99s stock and made a lot of mone=
y when the Paxlovid results were announced. Because Royal Caribbean=E2=80=
=99s stock=C2=A0did<em>=C2=A0</em>go up 8% that day. It was maybe not=C2=A0=
<em>the most obvious thing in the world=C2=A0</em>that Royal Caribbean woul=
d go up because Paxlovid worked, but nor was it all that=C2=A0surprising; i=
f you were paying attention to the world, you could have had some thought p=
rocess like =E2=80=9Cfew businesses were hit harder by Covid than cruises, =
and a cure for Covid is going to make it easier for people to go back on cr=
uise ships, so Royal Caribbean should go up a lot.=E2=80=9D And you would h=
ave been right and made a lot of money.</p>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">This is sometimes called =E2=80=9Cshadow tradi=
ng,=E2=80=9D using your inside information about one company (say, your emp=
loyer) to make informed trades on some other company that will also be affe=
cted by the news.</p>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">But would you have gotten arrested? Well! Well=
. We have <a href=3D"https://link.mail.bloombergbusiness.com/click/34412285=
.257387/aHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuYmxvb21iZXJnLmNvbS9vcGluaW9uL2FydGljbGVzLzIwMjEtMDg=
tMjMvc3BhYy1zdWl0LWxlYWRzLXRvLXNwYXJjcz9jbXBpZD1CQkQwMjIwMjRfTU9ORVlTVFVGRi=
Z1dG1fbWVkaXVtPWVtYWlsJnV0bV9zb3VyY2U9bmV3c2xldHRlciZ1dG1fdGVybT0yNDAyMjAmd=
