ottom-color: #000000; border-bottom-style: solid; background-color: #ccc;">=
  talked</a> a few <a href=3D"https://link.mail.bloombergbusiness.com/click=
/34412285.257387/aHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuYmxvb21iZXJnLmNvbS9vcGluaW9uL2FydGljbGVzLz=
